data.description: NO HOA!!! Absolutely gorgeous home with Beautiful open floor plan. Large family room features gas fireplace and opens into a welcoming dining room with access to the large backyard and beautiful new deck for outdoor entertainment. Back inside the kitchen features beautiful cabinets, nice countertops. Off kitchen and down the hall is the guest bedroom and additional second bathroom and 3 bedroom. The large master bedroom and extended master bath with nice tile shower. You must see this home. Plenty of space and did I say NO HOA!!!!
